    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions with NIH predictions within 18% of experimental values, and the RH index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all evaluated operating points. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
